# The dashboard has 6 tabs:

# Overview — live stats and activity log
# Images & Photos — replace tomb portrait, hero background, gallery photos 1–3, and logo (all instant, no page reload)
# Icons & UI — change any emoji icon via click-to-edit or the Quick Emoji Replace tool using element IDs
# Hero & Backgrounds — upload real photo to replace the cemetery SVG, adjust overlay darkness with a slider
# Platform Text — edit headline, subtext, deceased name, dates, and epitaph live
# Users — view registered families, resend invites, manage access
